race.comment: They'll go like the clappers in this. FORMAL (7) lines up for the in form Doyle stable and brings NSW form into the mix. He wasn't far away first-up at Wyong when running on from beyond midfield and he's sure to have come on from that performance. Looks well placed here on recent ratings and he can go one better today. BUNDELLA (12) is a last-start winner who again gets the deadly Gollan/Jones combination. Top-three contender on that sort of form. SHOT OF WHISKEY (3) has finished runner-up at his past three starts and is knocking on the door of another win. Include from the favourable draw. PARETO (1) makes some appeal with the 3kg claim.
